## Key design decisions
- Pipeline branching routes by VideoType from signal_assessment
- ExpertInsight uses heuristic regex patterns (no LLM call)
- Combined dashboard deduplicates macro by indicator, stocks by ticker
- Pipeline extractors wrapped in try/except for resilience
- analyze-all creates per-channel output subdirectories
- Cache TTL defaults to 7 days; stale entries trigger re-fetch attempt

